      <h3>Collect Observations</h3>
      <p>After creating a session record, you are ready to start observing.</p>
      <p>When you are ready to start, click the "Start Timer" button to begin.  At this point, the timer will start counting down by the interval you included in the sessions create form.</p>
      <p class="underline">Time Interval Indicators</p>
      <p>There are two indicators for time remaining in a given interval.  The first lists the number of seconds remaining before the response is recorded.  The second is a time bar which decreases in size as the interval comes to an end.  This bar also changes color from green to red depending on the time remaining in an interval.</p>
